I created my infographic using Canva, a free online design tool. My design explains the concept of digital literacy, useful tools for students, safe internet practices, and professional online presence.
I used simple icons and colors to make it visually appealing and easy to understand.
The infographic highlights how digital literacy helps students use the internet responsibly and build a professional identity.
One interesting part was selecting the right layout and icons to represent ideas clearly. 
The most difficult part was organizing all information in a single page without making it look crowded.
Overall, this task helped me understand the importance of digital skills in academics and daily life.
